modShortDescription: This mod adds a quick dirt bike. Only one seat. Same storage as bicycle. Unlocks with Grease Monkey 3. Decent fuel mileage, but low capacity.
modDescription:
This mod adds a quick dirt [bike](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-bike/). And no neighbors to complain about it! Only one seat. Same storage as a bicycle. Unlocks with Grease Monkey 3\. Decent fuel mileage, but low capacity.

## Changelog

Added new engine/horn sounds.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A19/tree/master/Dirt%20Bike)** for A19  
**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/bdubyah/Mods---A18/tree/master/Dirt%20Bike)** for A18

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11875-bdubyahs-modlets/).
